OL,3,CLeaseholders in England and Wales to
OL,4,Chave ground rent capped at #250
OL,6,FGround rents will be capped at #250 a
OL,7,Fyear in England and Wales as part of
OL,8,Fchanges to the leasehold system
OL,9,Fannounced by the government.
OL,11,FNew leasehold flats will also be
OL,12,Fbanned, while existing leaseholders
OL,13,Fwill be given the right to switch to
OL,14,Fcommonhold in a bid to give homeowners
OL,15,Fgreater control over their properties.
