OL,6,FMaking the major announcement in a
OL,7,Fvideo posted on TikTok, Prime Minister
OL,8,FSir Keir Starmer said: "I've spoken to
OL,9,Fso many people who say this will make
OL,10,Fa difference to them worth hundreds of
OL,11,Fpounds.
OL,13,F"That's really important because the
OL,14,Fcost of living is the single most
OL,15,Fimportant thing across the country."
