OL,3,CLeaseholders in England and Wales to
OL,4,Chave ground rent capped at #250
OL,6,FIt comes after backbenchers, including
OL,7,Fformer deputy prime minister Angela
OL,8,FRayner, urged the government to stick
OL,9,Fto Labour's manifesto promise to
OL,10,Ftackle "unregulated and unaffordable
OL,11,Fground rent charges" amid concerns the
OL,12,Fmove could impact pension funds.
OL,14,FWriting in the Guardian earlier this
OL,15,Fmonth, she said ministers were
OL,16,F"subjected to furious lobbying from
OL,17,Fwealthy investors" trying to water
OL,18,Fdown the commitment and warned people
OL,19,Fmay lose faith if the party could not
OL,20,Ffix the "obvious injustice" with a cap.
