OL,6,FLabour MPs have also previously urged
OL,7,Fministers to go further than ending
OL,8,Fnew leasehold flats by scrapping the
OL,9,Fsystem entirely.
OL,11,FHousing Secretary Steve Reed said the
OL,12,Fgovernment was committed to reducing
OL,13,Fground rents to zero and scrapping
OL,14,Fleaseholds entirely, but this would
OL,15,Fhave to happen "over time".
OL,17,FAsked what the timeframe would be for
OL,18,Fachieving this, he told Sky News
OL,19,Fministers would "be able to announce
OL,20,Fthat when we announce the results of
OL,21,Fthe consultation".
